    "body": "<!-- markdownlint-disable -->\n\n## Purpose\nFA4 is now the default FA version for Blackwell. However, it is not batch invariant. Thus, when batch invariance is enabled, fallback to FA2.\n\n## Test Plan\nRun batch invariant tests before and after the changes in this PR on a B200:\n\n```\nVLLM_LOGGING_LEVEL=INFO CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=4 VLLM_TEST_SEED=42 pytest tests/v1/determinism/test_batch_invariance.py::test_logprobs_bitwise_batch_invariance_bs1_vs_bsN[FLASH_ATTN] -s\n```\n\n## Test Result\nBefore:\n```\n(EngineCore_DP0 pid=3849625) INFO 03-04 23:06:32 [gpu_model_runner.py:4255] Starting to load model Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B...\n(EngineCore_DP0 pid=3849625) INFO 03-04 23:06:32 [cuda.py:368] Using AttentionBackendEnum.FLASH_ATTN backend.\n(EngineCore_DP0 pid=3849625) INFO 03-04 23:06:32 [flash_attn.py:587] Using FlashAttention version 4\n\n...\n\n====================================================== short test summary info =======================================================\nFAILED tests/v1/determinism/test_batch_invariance.py::test_logprobs_bitwise_batch_invariance_bs1_vs_bsN[FLASH_ATTN] - Failed: Batch invariance violated in 6/128 prompts. See output above for details.\n================================================== 1 failed, 20 warnings in 42.97s ===================================================\n```\n\nAfter\n```\n(EngineCore_DP0 pid=3843202) INFO 03-04 23:04:29 [gpu_model_runner.py:4255] Starting to load model Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B...\n(EngineCore_DP0 pid=3843202) WARNING 03-04 23:04:29 [fa_utils.py:118] Cannot use FA version 4 with batch invariance, defaulting to FA version 2.\n(EngineCore_DP0 pid=3843202) INFO 03-04 23:04:29 [cuda.py:368] Using AttentionBackendEnum.FLASH_ATTN backend.\n(EngineCore_DP0 pid=3843202) INFO 03-04 23:04:29 [flash_attn.py:587] Using FlashAttention version 2\n\n...\n\n================================================== 1 passed, 18 warnings in 31.67s ===================================================\n```\n\n---\n<details>\n<summary> Essential Elements of an Effective PR Description Checklist </summary>\n\n- [X] The purpose of the PR, such as \"Fix some issue (link existing issues this PR will resolve)\".\n- [X] The test plan, such as providing test command.\n- [X] The test results, such as pasting the results comparison before and after, or e2e results\n- [ ] (Optional) The necessary documentation update, such as updating `supported_models.md` and `examples` for a new model.\n- [ ] (Optional) Release notes update. If your change is user facing, please update the release notes draft in the [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YyVqrgX4gHTtrstbq8oWUImOyPCKSGnJ7xtTpmXzlRs/edit?tab=t.0).\n</details>\n\n",
